@NextHorizont_HostAddress = https://localhost:7194
@AdminUsername = admin
@AdminPassword = admin123

### 1. Login y Obtener JWT Token
# @name loginRequest
POST {{NextHorizont_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "{{AdminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{AdminPassword}}"
}

### 2. Capturar Token en Variable (Si usas la extensión REST Client de VS Code o Visual Studio 2022)
@token = {{loginRequest.response.body.token}}

### 3. Crear una nueva Ubicación / Mesa (Requiere Token)
POST {{NextHorizont_HostAddress}}/api/locations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "name": "Mesa 10",
  "type": "Mesa",
  "capacity": 4,
  "areaId": "AQUI_PONES_EL_ID_DEL_AREA"
}

### 4. Crear un Producto (Requiere Token)
POST {{NextHorizont_HostAddress}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "name": "Hamburguesa Doble Carne",
  "price": 15.50,
  "categoryId": "AQUI_PONES_EL_ID_DE_CATEGORIA"
}

### 5. Consultar Órdenes Activas (Requiere Token)
GET {{NextHorizont_HostAddress}}/api/orders/active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
